content: Extremely realistic and easy to use

Smooth and accurate (for a slide rule) and quite fun to play around with. Would be 5 stars without the forced auto- rotation. I'd prefer if the app respected my phone's auto- rotate setting, or at least some option to enable that
Purchased the Pro Version for a Moto G6. Over a two-day period I have not been able to download via WiFi and/or cell data.
replyContent: Hello, I'm sorry you are having this issue. Downloads are handled by the Google Play Store, maybe you can contact them to assist you with the problem. Make sure you have enough free space in your device to install the app.

content: Gets stuck?
replyContent: Hi, I'm sorry you had this issue. Could you contact us at contact@daosoftware.net and tell what device brand and model you are using? Thank you!

content: Very easy to use. But my phone has a notch on top of my screen so I can't see and press the middle two buttons. It will be btter to make the buttons bigger or relocate them.
Great for practicing when out and about.
Very useful. Very cleaver!
works great, use it all the time for teaching
Awesome app!
I like this app very much, and it does everything I need it to do. But, It is not compatible with the S-Pen on my Note 8. I would go for 5 stars if it worked with the pen.
replyContent: Hi! Thanks for your feedback. We will look into ways of making the app work with the S-Pen. Keep flying!

content: Awesome app to use while I'm in flight school, especially in conjunction with my EFB app. Only gripe is the entire E6B doesn't rotate so I would have to manually rotate my entire device to look at the numbers at the 3 to 9 positions. A rotation by moving only the upper part where it says "flight computer" to rotate the whole e6b would be perfect I think. Great job otherwise
replyContent: Hi, thank you for the feedback! We'll look into ways of making it possible on future releases. Have great flights!

content: Once installed it would not open so tried a second time. No luck so regretably have uninstalled. Since writing my original review I found a problem with my tablet which I cured by powering off then on again then reloading the app. It is now fully functioning and I now rate it five star.
replyContent: Hello, I'm sorry to hear that. Did you try the free version? Did it work? Do you have free space on your device? This is the first report of that kind that we had. Please feel free to contact us at contact@daosoftware.net

content: This app works great. One suggestion:  I use this on a newer phone with no issues, but on my samsung note 8.0 tablet the precision of the touch screen makes it difficult to adjust the wheel sometimes. An on screen tappable button option that can be engaged, like the lock button, for more precise adjusments would make it easier to move without passing the desired values.
This is getting better and better. Useful and accurate. Friendly interface and easy to use. Excellent work
Works well
Make a provision to lock the calculator ,so that one can enlarge and see the values without disturbing the initial settings...WILL GIVE 5 STRS FOR THIS FEATURE
replyContent: Hi! The new version just came up with a locking feature. Thank you for your feedback.
